nonmem.utils 0.1.0
  • Reference

    pull_name

    pull_name.Rd

    Pull Name from data Type field

    pull_name(type, meta_data = NULL)

    Arguments

    type

    Type of variable to retrieve

    meta_data

    A data.frame of meta data

    Examples

    # Dictionary
meta_data <- readr::read_csv(
system.file("template-dictionary.csv", package = "nonmem.utils"),
na = c("NA", "N/A", "", ".")
)
